    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "**Full script that generated the error**\r\n\r\n```\r\ngmt begin figure1 png\r\n    gmt set MAP_ANNOT_OBLIQUE=2\r\n    gmt set MAP_ANNOT_OFFSET_PRIMARY=1c\r\n    gmt basemap -JS0/-90/80/5c -R-180/180/-90/-80 -Bxa30f30g30 -Byf2.5g2.5\r\ngmt end show\r\n```\r\n\r\n![figure1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3974108/164589898-101a3e3f-5043-4143-af4d-8544928baada.png)\r\n\r\n**System information**\r\n\r\n* Operating system: Linux\r\n* GMT version (`gmt --version`): `6.4.0_56d4642_2022.04.21`\r\n",
